    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) Pridie lune qui est de mense aprilis. In presencia <rs key="Boni_viri/Boni_homines">bo[norum
                            hom]inum</rs> quorum nomina subter leguntur. Per lingnum quod in suis
                        tenebat manibus <persName key="#Judicial_breve #siblingOf #childOf"><name ref="Gandulfus/de Gusiago">Gandulfus</name></persName> et
                        <persName key="#Judicial_breve #siblingOf #childOf"><name ref="Ardicionus/de Gusiago">Ardizionus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">fratres</rs>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs>
                        <persName key="parentOf"><name ref="Maginfredus">Maifredi</name></persName> de loco <placeName ref="#places/4438">Gusiago</placeName>
                        fecerunt <rs key="#Judicial_breve">finem et refutacionem</rs> pro XX sollidos Mediolanensis adversus domnum
                        <persName key="#Monks #Monasteries #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Martinus/monacus Padolinorensis">Martinum</name></persName> 
                        et <persName key="#Monks #Monasteries #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Heinricus/monacus Padolinorensis">Einricum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monagos</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monks #Monasteries #Judicial_breve" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti</orgName> morantes in <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cellula</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Cells/hermitages" ref="#juridical_persons/2066">Sancti Vitis</orgName> que sita est in loco
                        <placeName key="#Cells/hermitages" ref="#places/2475">Methule</placeName>, de <rs key="Albergaria/gifori">albergaria</rs> et de omni
                        condicione seu eciam de ipsa terra quam pater supradictorum fratrum dedit
                        suprascripte ecclesie Sancti Vitis in comutacionis nomine; eo videlicet modo
                        ut ipsi suprascripti fratres neque illorum heredes aut aliqua hab heis
                        aposita persona non habeant potestatem agendi vel causandi aut per placitum
                        [ ... ] gandi suprascriptos monagos vel in locum illorum sucesores eidem
                        ecclesie Sancti Vitis fruentes aut quibus ipsi dederint de albergaria et de
                        qualibet [co]nditione seu de ipsa terra. Quod si hoc fecerint tunc
                        supradicti fratres tam per se quam per suos heredes suprascriptis monagis
                        suisque suctesoribus <rs key="#Penalty">penam C solidorum</rs> promiserunt et tacitos
                        permanere. Actum est hoc in <rs key="Collegiate_churches">calonica</rs> <orgName key="#Mother_churches #Dioecesis Collegiate_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1425">Sancte Marie 
                            <placeName key="#Mother_churches #Dioecesis Collegiate_churches" ref="#places/9">Brixiensis</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Mother_churches #Dioecesis">ecclesie</rs></orgName>. <rs key="#Witness">Ibi fuerunt</rs>:
                        <persName key="Boni_viri/Boni_homines #Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Milo/de Musculina">Milo</name></persName> 
                        et <persName key="Boni_viri/Boni_homines #Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Hugo/de Musculina">Ugo</name></persName>
                        de <placeName ref="#places/4439">Musculina</placeName> [e]t <persName key="Boni_viri/Boni_homines #Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Artusius/de Calcinato">Artusius</name></persName> 
                            et <persName key="Boni_viri/Boni_homines #Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Leo/de Calcinato">Leo</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4440">Calcinato</placeName>
                        et <persName key="Boni_viri/Boni_homines #Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Gherardus/Fustignum/de Medole">Girardus Fustignum</name></persName> de
                        Methole et <persName key="Boni_viri/Boni_homines #Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Gherardus/de Calcaria">Girardus</name></persName> 
                                de Calcaria et <persName key="Boni_viri/Boni_homines #Witness #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Hugo/de Saloto">Ugo</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4441">Saloto</placeName>. Ab incarnacione domini
                        nostri Iesu Christi milesimo centesimo vigesimo primo. (S.) Ego
                        <persName key="#Judge #Writer #Judicial_breve"><name ref="Gebizo/iudex">Gebizo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> rogatus <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
